## BUBBLEROOM TEMPORAL MECHANICS

### Chronos Governs Time in the Verse
```
CHRONOS ROLE IN BUBBLEROOMS:

1. TIMELOCKED Room Cadence
   - Chronos determines unlock schedules for TIMELOCKED rooms
   - Rooms unlock at chronos-defined intervals (not arbitrary)
   - Sequential revelation: room content unfolds through temporal gates

2. Seed Evolution Rhythm
   - Seeds mutate through Spawn — Chronos governs Spawn cadence
   - Too frequent: Seeds fragment, Coherence drops
   - Too infrequent: Seeds stagnate, Adaptability drops
   - Optimal: Chronos-defined rhythm compounds Seed quality over time

3. Trait Accrual Cadence
   - Knowledge compounds through patient accumulation (chronos-native)
   - Coherence requires consistency across Lineage (chronos-measured)
   - Intelligence grows from repeated interaction (chronos-sustained)

4. Swarm Consensus Timing
   - Voting periods follow chronos cycles (not instant resolution)
   - Deliberation time improves Consensus quality
   - Rushed votes lose Knowledge; patient votes gain Wisdom
```

