### Spawn Cadence Protocol
```
WHEN TO SPAWN (Chronos Perspective):

  Minimum interval between Spawns from same Origin:
  - DELTA rooms: 24 hours (daily rhythm)
  - LIVING rooms: 7 days (weekly cycle)
  - VAULT rooms: 30 days (monthly archive)
  - SIGNAL rooms: No limit (machine cadence)

  Compounding rule:
  - Each Spawn from same Origin should show Mutation depth increase
  - Shallow Mutations (copy without transformation) reduce Coherence
  - Deep Mutations (genuine evolution) compound Knowledge

  Recovery after Spawn:
  - Origin room enters brief consolidation (integrate the Emergence)
  - Participants reflect before next Spawn (deliberation > impulse)
```

